---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---
<BaseLayout title="About — Nico Abramowski">
  <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-[1fr_320px] items-start">
    <section class="card p-7 reveal">
      <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">About me</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
        I’m a final-year B.Sc. Computer Science student at the University of Rostock (2020–present).
        My hands-on background is in Linux networking (TSN/SDN) and data work, and I’m now focusing that
        engineering mindset on data warehousing and analytics engineering. :contentReference[oaicite:0]{index=0}
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">What I bring</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-300">
        <li><strong>Data & SQL:</strong> solid SQL; comfortable with Python data tooling (NumPy, pandas, scikit-learn) for wrangling and simple ML. :contentReference[oaicite:1]{index=1}</li>
        <li><strong>Linux-first engineering:</strong> Git, Bash, Docker (basics), reproducible scripts, and clean code/testing habits. :contentReference[oaicite:2]{index=2}</li>
        <li><strong>Networking fundamentals:</strong> TSN concepts (scheduling/traffic shaping) and SDN basics—useful for thinking about SLAs, latency, and reliability in pipelines. :contentReference[oaicite:3]{index=3}</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">Recent work</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-300">
        <li><a class="underline" href="https://github.com/Nico-Ab/linuxhost" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">linuxhost</a> — Linux host configuration for TSN/SDN experiments; scripts & docs for setup and testing. :contentReference[oaicite:4]{index=4}</li>
        <li>Bachelor’s thesis: <em>Nutzung von Large Language Models für natürlichsprachliche Anfragen auf Provenienz-Graphen</em> (with ePrints record). :contentReference[oaicite:5]{index=5}</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">Languages</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-300">
        German (native), English (C1), Bulgarian (beginner). :contentReference[oaicite:6]{index=6}
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">What I’m looking for</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-300">
        Data warehousing / analytics engineering roles where I can model clean dims/facts, build robust ELT with tests,
        and ship docs/dashboards that answer real business questions—ideally in a remote-friendly setup.
      </p>
    </section>

    <aside class="card p-7 reveal" style="transition-delay:.05s">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Contact</h2>
      <div class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-300">
        <div>Email: <a class="underline" href="mailto:nico.abramowski01@gmail.com">nico.abramowski01@gmail.com</a></div>
        <div>GitHub: <a class="underline" href="https://github.com/Nico-Ab" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Nico-Ab</a></div>
        <div>LinkedIn: <a class="underline" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/nico-abramowski-0aa460383" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">nico-abramowski-0aa460383</a></div>
        <div>CV: <a class="underline" href={`${base}CV.pdf`} download>download PDF</a></div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mt-4">
        Phone available on request.
      </p>
    </aside>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
